    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>The links of this +1 chainmail are a dull, sickly white color that resembles old bone, and the suit's gauntlets are tipped with silver-black finger spikes. Once per day as a standard action, the wearer can ask one question of an undead creature or a destroyed undead creature's corpse, as if using speak with dead, except the target can only answer questions that pertain to events that occurred after it became undead.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +1 chainmail</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, speak with dead</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Gods",
